          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>No Tax Deductions for Sexual Harasser Buyouts Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the tax deduction for trade or business expenses to deny a deduction for payments made to any employee in connection with the termination of employment if a factor in the termination was sexual assault, sexual harassment, or any other sexual misconduct by the employee.</p>]]></text>
